{"id":93,"name":"الضحى","transliteration":"Ad-Duhaa","translation":"The Morning Hours","type":"meccan","total_verses":11,"verses":[{"id":1,"text":"وَٱلضُّحَىٰ","translation":"By the morning brightness","transliteration":"Waaldduha"},{"id":2,"text":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا سَجَىٰ","translation":"And [by] the night when it covers with darkness","transliteration":"Waallayli itha saja"},{"id":3,"text":"مَا وَدَّعَكَ رَبُّكَ وَمَا قَلَىٰ","translation":"Your Lord has not taken leave of you, [O Muhammad], nor has He detested [you]","transliteration":"Ma waddaAAaka rabbuka wama qala"},{"id":4,"text":"وَلَلۡأٓخِرَةُ خَيۡرٞ لَّكَ مِنَ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ","translation":"And the Hereafter is better for you than the first [life]","transliteration":"Walalakhiratu khayrun laka mina aloola"},{"id":5,"text":"وَلَسَوۡفَ يُعۡطِيكَ رَبُّكَ فَتَرۡضَىٰٓ","translation":"And your Lord is going to give you, and you will be satisfied","transliteration":"Walasawfa yuAAteeka rabbuka fatarda"},{"id":6,"text":"أَلَمۡ يَجِدۡكَ يَتِيمٗا فَـَٔاوَىٰ","translation":"Did He not find you an orphan and give [you] refuge","transliteration":"Alam yajidka yateeman faawa"},{"id":7,"text":"وَوَجَدَكَ ضَآلّٗا فَهَدَىٰ","translation":"And He found you lost and guided [you]","transliteration":"Wawajadaka dallan fahada"},{"id":8,"text":"وَوَجَدَكَ عَآئِلٗا فَأَغۡنَىٰ","translation":"And He found you poor and made [you] self-sufficient","transliteration":"Wawajadaka AAailan faaghna"},{"id":9,"text":"فَأَمَّا ٱلۡيَتِيمَ فَلَا تَقۡهَرۡ","translation":"So as for the orphan, do not oppress [him]","transliteration":"Faamma alyateema fala taqhar"},{"id":10,"text":"وَأَمَّا ٱلسَّآئِلَ فَلَا تَنۡهَرۡ","translation":"And as for the petitioner, do not repel [him]","transliteration":"Waamma alssaila fala tanhar"},{"id":11,"text":"وَأَمَّا بِنِعۡمَةِ رَبِّكَ فَحَدِّثۡ","translation":"But as for the favor of your Lord, report [it]","transliteration":"Waamma biniAAmati rabbika fahaddith"}]}
